data %>% 
  filter(bloodStatus != "half-blood") %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x = fct_recode(house,  = "Gryffindor",  = "Hufflepuff",
                             = "Ravenclaw",  = "Slytherin"),
             fill = fct_recode(bloodStatus,  = "muggle-born",  = "pure-blood")))+
  geom_bar(position = "fill")+
  geom_hline(yintercept = 0.5, linetype = "dashed", colour = "yellow3", linewidth = 1)+
  theme_bw()+ 
  labs(x = "", y = " ", fill = "")

data %>% 
  filter(course == 5) %>% 
  mutate(id = as.factor(id)) %>%
  ggplot()+
  geom_segment(aes(x = 0, xend = result, y = fct_reorder(id, result), 
                   yend = fct_reorder(id, result)))+
  geom_point(aes(result, fct_reorder(id, result), colour = fct_recode(wandCore, 
                                                                      `  ` = "dragon heartstring", 
                                                                      ` ` = "phoenix feather",
                                                                      ` ` = "unicorn hair")))+
  theme_bw()+
  labs(colour = "C  ")+
  scale_colour_manual(values = c("  " = "red2", 
                               " " = "yellow2", 
                               " " = "gray70"))+
  theme(axis.text.y = element_blank(),
        axis.title.y = element_blank(), 
        axis.ticks.y = element_blank())

theme_custom <- theme_bw()+ theme(
        axis.text  = element_text(size = 18),

        axis.title.x = element_text(size = 22), 
        axis.title.y = element_text(size = 20),
        legend.title = element_text(size = 20) )
